# CLAUDE.md

This file provides guidance to Claude Code (claude.ai/code) when working with code in this repository.

## Development Commands

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install
pnpm install

# Development server
npm run dev
pnpm dev

# Production build
npm run build
pnpm build

# Start production server
npm run start
pnpm start
```

## Development Environment

### Prerequisites
- Node.js (latest LTS)
- npm or pnpm
- TypeScript knowledge

### Key Development Tools
- Next.js 14 (App Router)
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- MDX for content

## Project Workflow

### Blog Post Management
- Blog posts are MDX files in `app/blog/posts/`
- Frontmatter required:
  ```mdx
  ---
  title: Post Title
  publishedAt: YYYY-MM-DD
  summary: Brief description
  image: optional-image-path
  ---
  ```

### Project Updates
- Modify project details in `app/projects/page.tsx`

## Code Architecture Principles

1. File-based routing with Next.js App Router
2. Static site generation for blog posts
3. MDX for rich content rendering
4. Tailwind CSS for styling
5. Modular component structure

## Performance and SEO Features

